  "texts": [
    "Then, we removed the duplicate studies and applied inclusion/exclusion criteria to the title and abstract of the articles.",
    "After this process, we eliminated a set of publications that were not relevant and obtained a second publication pool.",
    "Following that, we applied inclusion/exclusion criteria to the full texts of the articles, and after eliminating a set of irrelevant publications, we obtained a third publication pool.",
    "Finally, we applied backward and forward snowballing to a third publication pool and obtained two more relevant articles.",
    "As a result, we obtained 34 studies to analyze within the scope of our SLR study [16]. a."
